{
  "stem": "20609.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we saw all the-- the-- we saw the beautiful stores with all the Danish pastry, which, by the way, in Denmark it's not called Danish pastry.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's called Vienna bread.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was about 30 or 40.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But some of them had arrived earlier and were still coming.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so we were put up in a-- in a-- in a pension for a couple of days-- one of those [INAUDIBLE] you know, with breakfast.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we met every day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they gave us the orientation-- what we were going to do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they said we are now being assigned to-- to-- each person will be assigned to a farmer on different islands.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know Denmark is an island community.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so we were assigned to a place called Fyn, which was the middle island.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "F-Y-N.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was pronounced 'fern.' And this is the island where, actually, Hans Christian Andersen was born.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was born in the city of Odense, which was at that time only like 20 miles from where I was.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We landed, believe it or not-- the winter was so-- so strong that year at-- the ferries-- Denmark had ferry condition between the main island and all the different islands.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But even that part of-- was frozen up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So-- [DRINKS] for the first time in my life, we were sent-- we-- we took a plane.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was an official, Scandinavian airline system plane with one engine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- [LAUGHS] and I think it had like eight or ten, twelve passengers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we boarded the plane, and again this was big excitement.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'd never been on a plane.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- [LAUGHS] and we went there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It took like an hour and a half or something at most to get where we were going to go.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
